{"tid":1572203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"私了完爽完要冷靜 回想還擊初衷係咩","createTime":"2019-09-15T15:24:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T16:15:24.000Z","uid":19945,"like":32,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"be14d0f5875564ba2c58963aa8987c8149c4a670","tid":1572203,"uid":19945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:24:11.000Z","msg":"出氣/以牙還牙當然係重點<br />\n但記唔記得本身係想達到咩效果<br />\n講到底係要令藍屍驚唔敢再出離搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以下一步要開始反滲透<br />\n用藍屍account去藍屍集中營增加佢地恐懼<br />\n將被圍既片段不斷煲大<br />\n再留言嚇佢地地區活動都開始會私了<br />\n同對方派人搞我地作用一樣<br />\n記住睇完爽完一回事<br />\n我寧願無得再爽換無手足再比人搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac6126d9c2f4fb2a30768638690182d3a330943","tid":1572203,"uid":19945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:25:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1668ec75b314d027d86e134402a60ff7d1fbef5","tid":1572203,"uid":62714,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:27:35.000Z","msg":"想睇下星期個清潔行動會有幾多傻閪去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5362a4059b3109f2ab273ff12806741c8ac9888","tid":1572203,"uid":305794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:27:53.000Z","msg":"［極重要］全民錫春袋！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1572107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1572107</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d5d96eeb4babf4168b2517dd3f5c789c1f5adc89","tid":1572203,"uid":186845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:28:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9297894d5696ba56fb26da681ef33b88d1495276","tid":1572203,"uid":73089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:28:20.000Z","msg":"唔需要反省 諗點樣唔好俾人跟踪返屋企就得"},{"pid":"c546ca7cab71f527c7585c526f31a6f8e22cf528","tid":1572203,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:29:07.000Z